response: the Holy Grail

clue: During the meal Jesus predicts that this man will deny knowing him 3 times

response: Peter

clue: According to John, Satan entered this apostle during the Last Supper

response: Judas

clue: Traditionally the Last Supper is thought to have taken place on this day of the week

response: Thursday

